{
  "id": "adv_card_suz_06_03",
  "title": "成宮すず",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_corridor_night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "クリスマス二次会を始めますわよ！\n二人で眠気を吹き飛ばすのですわ！",
      "startTime": 3.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "いや、俺は眠たくないんだが……\n眠気を吹き飛ばすって、一体何をする気だ？",
      "startTime": 9.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "眠気覚ましにはカードゲームです！\n二人でババ抜きをやりますわよ！",
      "startTime": 16.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "二人でババ抜きって……楽しいのか？",
      "startTime": 18.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "次はこれで眠気を吹き飛ばすのですわ！",
      "startTime": 25,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "だから、俺は別に眠たくないんだが……",
      "startTime": 28.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "眠気覚ましに、この映画を観ましょう！\n千紗からオススメの映画を借りておいたのですわ！",
      "startTime": 35.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "それは……違う意味で眠れなくなりそうだな……",
      "startTime": 39.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_garden-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_garden-01-000-night",
      "startTime": 44.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "まだありますわよ！\n更にこれで眠気を吹き飛ばすのですわ！",
      "startTime": 47.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "眠気を吹き飛ばしたいのはすずだけだろ？\n俺は一緒にやらなくてもいいんじゃ……",
      "startTime": 54,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "夜空に向かって大声で歌いましょう！\n二人でクリスマスソングをデュエットしますわよ！",
      "startTime": 60.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "近所迷惑だ……勘弁してくれ……",
      "startTime": 64.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_corridor_night",
      "startTime": 69.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "まだまだ！　ですわ！　眠気覚ましにはカフェイン！\n濃いコーヒーを淹れますから、飲んでくださいまし！",
      "startTime": 75.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "コーヒーを飲むのはすずじゃないのか？",
      "startTime": 79.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "私は苦いのはちょっと……",
      "startTime": 82.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "ですから、私が眠くならないように\n{user}さんに飲んでもらいますわ！",
      "startTime": 89.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（もしかして、眠くて頭が回っていないのか？）\n（理屈がめちゃくちゃだ……）",
      "startTime": 95.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03-suz010.m4a",
      "text": "いろいろと試しましたが、やっぱり眠気覚ましには\n誰かとお喋りするのが一番ですわね",
      "startTime": 105.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03-suz011.m4a",
      "text": "こうして暖房の効いた部屋で、ぬくぬく温まりながら\n{user}さんと話していると……",
      "startTime": 113.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03-suz012.m4a",
      "text": "なんだか安心して、気が緩んできて……",
      "startTime": 116.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03-suz013.m4a",
      "text": "すやぁ……",
      "startTime": 122.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03-suz014.m4a",
      "text": "……はっ！　寝てませんから！\n全然眠くなんてありませんから！",
      "startTime": 127.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03-suz015.m4a",
      "text": "クリスマスは私が守ります！　私が起きている限り\nクリスマスは永遠に終わらないのですわー！",
      "startTime": 134.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "（……これはすずが寝るのも時間の問題だな）",
      "startTime": 138.5,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 12633.333333299986,
          "startTime": 151.1333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03-suz016.m4a",
      "text": "良い子のみなさ～ん！\nアイドルサンタ成宮すずが街にやって来ましたわよ～！",
      "startTime": 147.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03-suz017.m4a",
      "text": "星降る街に舞い降りたアイドルサンタが\nハッピーをお届けするのですわ～！",
      "startTime": 156,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03-suz018.m4a",
      "text": "良い子のみなさんにプレゼントを差し上げましょう\n私からの贈り物、受け取ってくれますわよね？",
      "startTime": 162.7666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2133.3333333000155,
          "startTime": 164.9
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "わ～い！　アイドルサンタさ～ん！\n俺にもプレゼントを下さ～い！",
      "startTime": 170.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03-suz019.m4a",
      "text": "特に良い子の{user}さんには特別に\n成宮すず専属マネージャーの権利を差し上げますわ",
      "startTime": 176.8333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "ありがたき幸せ～",
      "startTime": 181.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03-suz020.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルサンタ成宮すずは\nいつでもあなたの隣にいるのですわ",
      "startTime": 187.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03-suz021.m4a",
      "text": "……え？\nそういう私はプレゼントに何がほしいかですか？",
      "startTime": 192.1,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 12300.000000000011,
          "startTime": 204.4
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03-suz022.m4a",
      "text": "私の望みは……みなさんと過ごす幸せな時間が\n永遠に続きますように、ですわ！",
      "startTime": 202.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_corridor_noon",
      "startTime": 207.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03-suz023.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ……うふふ……\nアイドルサンタのお通りなのですわ～……",
      "startTime": 212.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03-suz024.m4a",
      "text": "……はっ！",
      "startTime": 216.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03-suz025.m4a",
      "text": "私、いつの間に寝ていましたの！？\n時計は……ああっ、もう朝ではありませんか！",
      "startTime": 220.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03-suz026.m4a",
      "text": "一生の不覚ですわ……\nクリスマスが終わってしまったのですわ……",
      "startTime": 229.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
