      "text": "楽しい夢を見ていたみたいだな\n寝ながら顔が笑っていたぞ",
      "startTime": 242.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03-suz028.m4a",
      "text": "なっ。レディの寝顔を眺めるなんて趣味が悪いのですわ\n見ていたのなら起こしてくださいまし",
      "startTime": 250.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
