      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03-suz029.m4a",
      "text": "え？　あ……リボンのついた箱が……\nこれって私へのクリスマスプレゼントですの？",
      "startTime": 265.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "メリークリスマス\n眠っている間にサンタが届けてくれたみたいだな",
      "startTime": 272.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03-suz030.m4a",
      "text": "サンタ……そうですわね\n眠らないとサンタは来てくれない……",
      "startTime": 281.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_03-suz031.m4a",
      "text": "朝起きたら枕元にプレゼントがあるように\nたとえクリスマスの夜が終わっても……",
      "startTime": 289.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
